token_info.description: This 3D model is created by Nikita Khudiakov as an exploration of architecture for Metaverse and can be used on different platforms. You can visit the virtual space using a link on the artist’s website. The file itself is a 3D model in .glb format. This NFT is available in 20 editions and I will manage a meetup  in this virtual space for owners of this NFT who will contact me after all 20 will be sold. Artist’s links - https://linktr.ee/voobrazhenie
